---
title: Unidirectional Data Flow (No Circular Dependencies)
---
%%{init: {'theme':'base'}}%%
flowchart LR
    subgraph External["🔵 External Sources (Read-Only)"]
        API[GitHub API<br/>Real-time metadata]
        Sheets[Google Sheets<br/>Curated lists]
        Jira[Jira Issues<br/>Project tracking]
    end
    
    subgraph Canonical["🟡 Canonical Storage (Single Source of Truth)"]
        Repos[(repositories.yml<br/>Synced data)]
        Merged[(merged_data.yml<br/>Combined sources)]
    end
    
    subgraph Generated["🟢 Generated Outputs (Read-Only)"]
        LIST[LIST.md<br/>Bullet format]
        TABLE[TABLE.md<br/>Table format]
        ARCHIVE[ARCHIVE.md<br/>Archived repos]
    end
    
    API ==>|sync| Repos
    Sheets -.->|optional| Repos
    Jira -.->|optional| Repos
    
    Repos ==>|load + merge| Merged
    Merged ==>|validate| Merged
    Merged ==>|generate| LIST
    Merged ==>|generate| TABLE
    Merged ==>|generate| ARCHIVE
    
    LIST -.x|NO FEEDBACK| Repos
    TABLE -.x|NO FEEDBACK| Repos
    ARCHIVE -.x|NO FEEDBACK| Repos
    
    style API fill:#2196f3,stroke:#1976d2,stroke-width:3px,color:#fff
    style Sheets fill:#4caf50,stroke:#388e3c,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style Jira fill:#4caf50,stroke:#388e3c,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style Repos fill:#ff9800,stroke:#f57c00,stroke-width:3px,color:#000
    style Merged fill:#ff9800,stroke:#f57c00,stroke-width:3px,color:#000
    style LIST fill:#4caf50,stroke:#388e3c,stroke-width:3px,color:#fff
    style TABLE fill:#4caf50,stroke:#388e3c,stroke-width:3px,color:#fff
    style ARCHIVE fill:#4caf50,stroke:#388e3c,stroke-width:3px,color:#fff

